('30', '10', 'assistant', '# **KG + VectorStore Answer - [Focused Response Directive]\n\nPlease follow these instructions when answering:\n• Answer ONLY the specific question asked - be precise and direct\n• Include ONLY information that is immediately relevant to this specific question\n• Exclude tangential details, background context, or loosely related information\n• Be concise while remaining comprehensive on the core topic\n• Prioritize clarity and relevance over exhaustive coverage\n\nUser''s Question: What is the CRR and PRR logic for order placement?**\n\n_Generated: 2025-10-22 07:42_\n\n## **Answer**\n\n**Direct Answer:**  \nCRR logic equals compliance-rule checks during order placement [KG: dataentity:order] [KG: compliance:qty_is_mandatory_totalorderamt_amount_based_orders]. The key CRR rule requires QTY to be mandatory with TOTALORDERAMT for amount-based orders [KG: compliance:qty_is_mandatory_totalorderamt_amount_based_orders]. PRR logic ties to product risk profile governance, influencing order placement via risk rating displays and validations [KG: dataentity:order] [KG: dataentity:product_risk_profile]. [1]\n\n**Key Points:**  \n• Point 1: CRR involves compliance validations on orders, including the mandatory QTY rule [KG: compliance:qty_is_mandatory_totalorderamt_amount_based_orders] [2]  \n• Point 2: PRR involves product risk profile governance; orders contain and are governed by the product risk profile [KG: dataentity:order] [KG: dataentity:product_risk_profile] [2]  \n• Point 3: Risk rating is displayed on Order and Product risk profile [KG: dataentity:risk_rating] [1]\n\n**Note:** The KG does not define CRR/PRR terms explicitly; CRR maps to compliance checks, PRR to risk-profile governance. [1]\n\n---\n\n## **Citations**\n\n_No citations available._\n', 'f28d889f-5582-4d29-bcf9-dd21bd8962ac', NULL, '{"domain":"wealth_management","vectorstore_id":"vs_689b49252a4c8191a12a1528a475fbd8","response_id":"f28d889f-5582-4d29-bcf9-dd21bd8962ac","is_conversational":false,"mode":"concise","processing_time_seconds":68.96,"request_id":"2321c8f1-4b54-475a-951a-d543df6ad556"}', '2025-10-22 07:42:37.629455'),
