('34', '10', 'assistant', '# **KG + VectorStore Answer - Context: This is a follow-up question in a conversation. Please maintain context from the previous discussion.\n\nQuestion: [Context-Aware Follow-up Question with Focus Directives]\n\nPrevious conversation history is provided for context. Please follow these instructions:\n\nSTEP 1 - Context Understanding:\n• Evaluate if this question contains pronouns or unclear references (e.g., "this", "it", "that", "these", "the above")\n• If such references exist, identify what they refer to based on the conversation history\n• Internally clarify the question to make it self-contained and explicit\n\nSTEP 2 - Focused Response Generation:\n• Answer ONLY the specific question asked - be precise and direct\n• Include ONLY information that is immediately relevant to this specific question\n• Exclude tangential details, background context, or loosely related information\n• Be concise while remaining comprehensive on the core topic\n• Prioritize clarity and relevance over exhaustive coverage\n\nUser''s Question: can you deep dive into how these risk profiles are asessed ?**\n\n_Generated: 2025-10-22 08:56_\n\n## **Answer**\n\n**Direct Answer:**  \n• Risk profiles are assessed via a Risk Profile Questionnaire evaluating willingness and ability to take risk <sup><a href="#cite-1">[1]</a></sup><sup><a href="#cite-2">[2]</a></sup> [KG: dataentity:product_risk_profile].  \n• The questionnaire has Personal Information and Suitability Assessment sections <sup><a href="#cite-1">[1]</a></sup><sup><a href="#cite-2">[2]</a></sup> [KG: dataentity:product_risk_profile].  \n• Answers yield a risk score and acceptable risk level <sup><a href="#cite-1">[1]</a></sup><sup><a href="#cite-2">[2]</a></sup> [KG: dataentity:product_risk_profile].  \n• If profiling is complete, the system shows the recommended risk profile <sup><a href="#cite-2">[2]</a></sup> [KG: dataentity:product_risk_profile]. <sup><a href="#cite-1">[1]</a></sup>\n\n**Key Points:**  \n• Point 1: Risk Profile Questionnaire evaluates willingness and ability to take risk <sup><a href="#cite-1">[1]</a></sup><sup><a href="#cite-2">[2]</a></sup> [KG: dataentity:product_risk_profile].  \n• Point 2: It includes Personal Information and Suitability Assessment sections <sup><a href="#cite-1">[1]</a></sup><sup><a href="#cite-2">[2]</a></sup> [KG: dataentity:product_risk_profile].  \n• Point 3: Outcomes yield risk score and recommended profile; complete profiling triggers recommendations <sup><a href="#cite-1">[1]</a></sup><sup><a href="#cite-2">[2]</a></sup> [KG: dataentity:product_risk_profile].\n\n**Note:** Context refers to HSBC-Intellect risk profiling within the PMS workflow <sup><a href="#cite-1">[1]</a></sup><sup><a href="#cite-2">[2]</a></sup> [KG: system:pms_app].\n\n---\n\n## **Citations**\n\n<a id="cite-1"></a>\n**[1]** → **Journey of Assessing Risk_Base_V1.0.pdf**\n\n<a id="cite-2"></a>\n**[2]** → **WQ_Journey of Planning for Financial Goals and Making Investmen...**\n\n<a id="cite-3"></a>\n**[3]** → **PAD Plan Journey_SGV5.0.pdf**\n\n\n---\n\n## **Sources by File**\n\n- **Journey of Assessing Risk_Base_V1.0.pdf** → [1]\n- **PAD Plan Journey_SGV5.0.pdf** → [3]\n- **WQ_Journey of Planning for Financial Goals and Making Investmen...** → [2]\n', 'f28d889f-5582-4d29-bcf9-dd21bd8962ac', '[{"filename":"Journey of Assessing Risk_Base_V1.0.pdf","file_id":"file-TJwTyfAdSu7L2mQckDVVMt","score":0.8065138909175542,"text":"Internal to HSBC and Intellect  Page 5 \\n \\n\\n\\n\\n   \\n \\n \\n\\n \\n\\n \\n\\n \\n\\n4. Process Flow \\n\\n4.1. Login \\n\\n1. The User enters their credentials and logs into the application \\n \\n\\n \\nScreen: Launch the application \\n\\n \\n\\n2. Once logged in, they can click on “Operation Office” to set up the risk profiling-related maintenance or “PMS” to  do \\nthe risk profiling for the customers \\n\\n \\n\\nInternal to HSBC and Intellect  Page 6 \\n \\n\\n\\n\\n   \\n \\n\\n \\nScreen: Select Operation Office \\n\\