('42', '15', 'assistant', '# **KG + VectorStore Answer - [Focused Response Directive]\n\nPlease follow these instructions when answering:\n• Answer ONLY the specific question asked - be precise and direct\n• Include ONLY information that is immediately relevant to this specific question\n• Exclude tangential details, background context, or loosely related information\n• Be concise while remaining comprehensive on the core topic\n• Prioritize clarity and relevance over exhaustive coverage\n\nUser''s Question: What reports are generated for clients?**\n\n_Generated: 2025-10-31 06:40_\n\n## **Answer**\n\n**Direct Answer:** Client-facing reports include Gain-Loss Report, Grandfathering Report, and Order Statement for Client.<sup><a href="#cite-2">[2]</a></sup> Consolidated Holding Report, Order Rejection Report, and SIP Due Report.<sup><a href="#cite-2">[2]</a></sup> Corporate Action for Client, SIP/SWP/STP For Client, Holding Report for Client, ELSS, and One Pager.<sup><a href="#cite-2">[2]</a></sup> Risk Profile reports are also generated for clients.<sup><a href="#cite-3">[3]</a></sup> <sup><a href="#cite-1">[1]</a></sup>\n\n**Key Points:**\n• Point 1: Client-facing reports include Gain-Loss Report, Grandfathering Report, and Order Statement for Client. <sup><a href="#cite-2">[2]</a></sup>  \n• Point 2: Additional client reports include Consolidated Holding Report, Order Rejection Report, and SIP Due Report. <sup><a href="#cite-2">[2]</a></sup>  \n• Point 3: Also, Corporate Action for Client, SIP/SWP/STP For Client, Holding Report for Client, ELSS, and One Pager. <sup><a href="#cite-2">[2]</a></sup>  \n• Point 4: Risk Profile reports are also generated for clients. <sup><a href="#cite-3">[3]</a></sup> [KG: dataentity:product_risk_profile]\n\n**Note:** The list reflects passages provided; actual reports may vary by system. <sup><a href="#cite-1">[1]</a></sup>\n\n---\n\n## **Citations**\n\n<a id="cite-1"></a>\n**[1]** → **WQ-Reports_V1.1_HSBC_CCV1.0.pdf**\n\n<a id="cit