 order under “Oder(s) in Pending State” (Will be renamed as Order(s) pending for \\n\\nsubmission) and click on “Submit”, system will trigger the OTP validation. \\n\\n \\n\\n3.9. If customer enters a wrong OTP, system will display “Invalid OTP”. \\n\\n3.10. Customer can click on “Resend OTP” to regenerate the OTP.  \\n\\n3.11. On clicking the “Resend OTP”, a new OTP will be generated and send to the customer’s registered mobile \\n\\nnumber. \\n\\n3.12. If customer enters wrong OTP successively for 3 times, then the order status will be updated as “Failed”. \\n\\n3.13. In order book, under “System Remarks”, the error message will be displayed as “Order could not be \\n\\nprocessed. Incorrect OTP entered successively for 3 times”. \\n\\n3.14. Customer has to reinitiate the order from starting again. \\n\\n9 \\n \\n\\n\\n\\n \\n\\n3.15. Customer will enter the OTP and click on “Validate OTP”. \\n\\n3.16. On successful validation system will call the “Fund Transfer API”. \\n\\n3.17. The order amount will be debited from the customers...","query":"[Focused Response Directive]\\n\\nPlease follow these instructions when answering:\\n• Answer ONLY the specific question asked - be precise and direct\\n• Include ONLY information that is immediately relevant to this specific question\\n• Exclude tangential details, background context, or loosely related information\\n• Be concise while remaining comprehensive on the core topic\\n• Prioritize clarity and relevance over exhaustive coverage\\n\\nUser''s Question: What is the full lifecycle of mutual funds order placement? requirements rules conditions","norm_score":0.8675822745000112,"relevance_score":0.6939756263187625},{"filename":"Sample WQ_Journey from Order Placement till Settlement - MF_HSBC_V1.1_CCV.1.0_Part 2.pdf","file_id":"file-FS9XM1NLVi3CYvgRVkbbcH","score":0.8066574196277593,"text":"3. User selects the desired investment account from the dropdown and can view the Folio Number. If the fund\\n\\nInternal to HSBC and 